<li><a href="/a-thin-dangerous-line">生死一息间</a></li>
</ul>
<div style="text-align:right">
<p><sub><a href="#toc">回到顶部</a></sub></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone series" style="background-color: #FFFFFF;">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<h1 id="toc39"><span>机动特遣队Omega-7（“Pandora's Box”-潘多拉之盒）</span></h1>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/task-forces/Omega7.jpg/small.jpg" alt="small.jpg" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<p><strong>特遣队任务：</strong> <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">机动特遣队Omega-7是一个实验性特遣队，通过与人形异常个体的合作来获取和收容异常，特别是SCP-076和SCP-105。</span>机动特遣队Omega-7已被解散和除役。本条目已经被记录和文档安全管理员下令删除。</p>
<p><strong>协助收容的项目：</strong><br />
<span style="text-decoration: line-through;"><a href="/scp-076">SCP-076</a></span><br />
<span style="text-decoration: line-through;"><a href="/scp-105">SCP-105</a></span><br />
